OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDefence Secretary Ben      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FWallace to call for more   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fmilitary spending over     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Defence Secretary Ben Wallace is set to
OL,6, issue a call for more spending on the  
OL,7, UK's armed forces in light of Russia's 
OL,8, invasion of Ukraine.                   
OL,10,FHe will give a speech on Tuesday - but 
OL,11,Fhas reportedly already asked the prime 
OL,12,Fminister to increase defence spending  
OL,13,Fto 2.5% of GDP by 2028.                
OL,15,FThe UK is currently spending around 2% 
OL,16,Fof GDP on defence, matching the target 
OL,17,Fset by the Nato for member nations.    
OL,19,FThe government announced an increase in
OL,20,Fmilitary spending in 2020.             
